title: Come Worry With Us! feat. Thee Silver Mt. Zion Memorial Orchestr
description:
Here's a companion piece to Come Worry With Us!, which you'll find
at https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/10251883

It downloads to the same folder.

This collects the wonderful outtakes from
(thirteen so far) in their order of publication, except that parts
of a conversation are grouped together, with #8 and #9 switched to
restore the flow of time.
